{"tid":564485,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網上留言罵官員　湖北婦遭行政拘留10天","createTime":"2018-02-18T04:54:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T05:03:53.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c189fc7964f3a8fb038d5c397bd923f8e89d5d7e","tid":564485,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:54:46.000Z","msg":"湖北武漢市有婦人4日前在網絡社交平台上留言「武漢市長滾」後，被當地警方拘留10日，事件引起輿論熱議。有內地律師向海外傳媒表示，警方是次有選擇性執法及濫用權力之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n網傳由武漢市公安局武昌分局發出的行政處罰決定書指出，市民丁文婷於周三（14日）凌晨在微博上留言抨擊武漢市長，被警方以「在微博上公開發表辱罵他人的言論，造成不良後果」為由，處行政拘留10天。據報丁文婷並非首次被警方盯上，她曾因「破壞選舉」被行政拘留5日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180217/bkncn-20180217200121044-0217_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180217%2Fbkncn-20180217200121044-0217_05011_001.html&d=ePnc8nuz0lVNRm5%2BXZzthwHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=a6543f6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180217/bkncn-20180217200121044-0217_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b02c8521e7d7efad321d7dab1829b771e13e61bc","tid":564485,"uid":3037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:56:32.000Z","msg":"好快到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f88f7e1f2363bfd30641a6e9c8dc9854599886","tid":564485,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T05:03:53.000Z","msg":"好快到香港！"}]}